'''巴卜之戰'''是包括[[自由叙利亚军|自由叙利亚军]]屬下團體在內的[[敘利亞反對派|敘利亞反對派]]與[[土耳其|土耳其]]軍隊聯合發起的一次攻勢，以奪取被[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]佔領的敘利亞[[阿勒颇省|阿勒颇省]]城市[[巴卜|巴卜]]。被土耳其政府敵視的[[敘利亞民主力量|敘利亞民主力量]]曾有意搶在自由軍和土耳其軍之前攻佔巴卜。

2017年2月23日，土耳其領導的聯軍攻佔巴卜。

==2016年==
[[File:Walbab3.png|thumb]]
敘反對派與土耳其的聯軍開始攻勢後，很快進抵巴卜外圍，<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2016-11/18/c_129368229.htm |title=“打脸”？美国称不支持土耳其在叙利亚行动 |publisher=新華網 |date=2016-11-18 |accessdate=2017-01-23 |archive-date=2017-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202014456/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2016-11/18/c_129368229.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>與此同時，[[敘利亞民主力量|敘利亞民主力量]]攻佔巴卜以東的7條村。<ref name=arima>[http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=54574 The Syria Democratic Forces are trying to besiege al-Arima and factions of "Euphrates Shield" advance in the vicinity of al-Bab with clashes on its frontiers] {{Wayback|url=http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=54574 |date=20161220214852 }}, 2016-11-13.</ref><ref name=four>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-rebels-storm-isis-stronghold-al-bab-northern-aleppo-map/|title=Syrian rebels storm ISIS stronghold of al-Bab in northern Aleppo - Map|first=Chris|last=Tomson|date=2016-11-15|publisher=|accessdate=2016-11-16|archive-date=2017-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171222120629/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-rebels-storm-isis-stronghold-al-bab-northern-aleppo-map/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

土耳其領導的聯軍在巴卜遇到伊斯蘭國頑強抵抗，久攻不下。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2017-01/21/c_129455482.htm |title=俄土首次在叙利亚联合空袭 摧毁36个IS目标 |publisher=新華網 |date=2017-01-21 |accessdate=2017-01-23 |archive-date=2017-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202014500/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2017-01/21/c_129455482.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

11月23日，敘民主力量攻佔Arima村。土耳其軍向該地區由敘民主力量控制的村莊發炮。<ref name=arimahr>{{cite web|url=http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=55427 |title=A large number of injuries in the continued "Turkish Shelling" on the control areas of Manbij Military Council |work=Syria HR |date=2016-11-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161202210405/http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=55427 |archivedate=2016-12-02 }}</ref><ref name=three>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/huge-three-way-battle-unfolds-near-al-bab-parties-seize-territory-day/|title=Huge three-way battle unfolds near al-Bab as all parties seize territory in the same day|first=Chris|last=Tomson|date=2016-11-23|publisher=|access-date=2017-01-25|archive-date=2017-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171222051257/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/huge-three-way-battle-unfolds-near-al-bab-parties-seize-territory-day/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=arimahr2>{{cite web|url=http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=55445|title=Human losses in Turkish forces and in aerial bombardment on al-Arima|work=Syrian Observatory of Human Rights|date=24 November 2016|access-date=2017-01-25|archive-date=2016-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161202210407/http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=55445|dead-url=no}}</ref>

11月25日至27日間，敘民主力量從伊斯蘭國手上攻佔巴卜以西的兩個村莊，而敘反對派攻佔巴卜以東的3個村莊。在巴卜以東兩個由敘民主力量控制的村莊遭到敘反對派攻擊。親敘利亞政府的部隊從伊斯蘭國手上攻佔巴卜以西的4個村莊。<ref name="Alleyes">{{cite web |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/syria-civil-war-al-bab-turkey-kurds-free-syrian-army-assad-raqqa-a7443411.html |title=Inside the final push against Isis |date=2016-11-28 |publisher= |access-date=2017-01-25 |archive-date=2018-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180106072422/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/syria-civil-war-al-bab-turkey-kurds-free-syrian-army-assad-raqqa-a7443411.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

11月28日，敘政府軍從土耳其支持的敘反對派手上攻佔巴卜以西的一個村莊，距離巴卜市不到5公里。<ref name="FirstFSA">{{cite web |url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-captures-first-village-turkish-backed-rebels-outskirts-al-bab/ |title=Syrian Army captures first village from Turkish-backed rebels on the outskirts of al-Bab |first=Chris |last=Tomson |date=2016-11-29 |publisher= |access-date=2017-01-23 |archive-date=2018-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224220900/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/syrian-army-captures-first-village-turkish-backed-rebels-outskirts-al-bab/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/CivilWarMap/status/803366408784670722|title=Syrian Civil War Map on Twitter|publisher=|access-date=2017-01-25|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108135844/https://twitter.com/CivilWarMap/status/803366408784670722|dead-url=no}}</ref>

土耳其軍方宣稱在2016年12月21日一日內，土耳其軍打死近140名伊斯蘭國武裝分子。土耳其於12月24日稱土耳其戰機在[[阿勒頗|阿勒頗]]市東北20公里處炸死68名伊斯蘭國武裝分子。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.voanews.com/a/families-of-turkish-soldiers-burned-by-is-search-for-answers/3649497.html |title=Turkish Military: Rebels, Airstrikes Kill Nearly 70 Militants in Northern Syria |publisher=美國之音 |date=2016-12-24 |accessdate=2017-01-23 |archive-date=2017-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170622021049/https://www.voanews.com/a/families-of-turkish-soldiers-burned-by-is-search-for-answers/3649497.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2016年12月26日，親敘利亞政府的消息來源稱[[俄羅斯空軍|俄羅斯空軍]]首度在敘利亞境內直接支援土耳其軍。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/russian-jets-carry-airstrikes-aid-turkish-army-aleppos-al-bab/|title=Russian jets carry out airstrikes to aid Turkish Army in Aleppo's Al-Bab|publisher=Al-Masdar News|date=26 December 2016|accessdate=26 December 2016|archive-date=2017-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171010121909/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/russian-jets-carry-airstrikes-aid-turkish-army-aleppos-al-bab/|dead-url=no}}</ref>土耳其副總理[[努曼·庫爾圖爾穆什|努曼·庫爾圖爾穆什]]否認該報道。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailysabah.com/war-on-terror/2016/12/28/fsa-fighters-evacuated-from-aleppo-to-boost-fight-in-al-bab|title=FSA fighters evacuated from Aleppo to boost fight in al-Bab|publisher=Daily Sabah|date=27 December 2016|accessdate=27 December 2016|archive-date=2017-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171222162711/https://www.dailysabah.com/war-on-terror/2016/12/28/fsa-fighters-evacuated-from-aleppo-to-boost-fight-in-al-bab|dead-url=no}}</ref>12月27日，1,000名土耳其軍人和2,000名敘反對派人員抵達前方增援。<ref name=TSKFSAreinfocrements>{{cite web|url=http://www.yenisafak.com/en/news/turkish-commandos-enter-al-bab-2587222|title=Turkish commandos enter al-Bab|publisher=Yeni Şafak|date=2016-12-27|accessdate=2016-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161228032644/http://www.yenisafak.com/en/news/turkish-commandos-enter-al-bab-2587222|archive-date=2016-12-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

一名土耳其官員在2016年12月29日稱[[俄羅斯空軍|俄羅斯空軍]]首度攻擊巴卜的伊斯蘭國目標，而土耳其軍正在進攻巴卜市的北部和西部。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailysabah.com/syrian-crisis/2016/12/29/russian-jets-strike-daesh-targets-in-syrias-al-bab-for-first-time|title=Russian jets strike Daesh targets in Syria's al-Bab for first time|publisher=Daily Sabah|date=29 December 2016|accessdate=29 December 2016|archive-date=2019-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190328065920/https://www.dailysabah.com/syrian-crisis/2016/12/29/russian-jets-strike-daesh-targets-in-syrias-al-bab-for-first-time|dead-url=no}}</ref>土耳其外長表示土耳其與俄羅斯並無聯合行動。<ref name=MEERussia>{{cite web|url=http://www.middleeasteye.net/news/russia-bombs-islamic-state-held-town-syria-aids-turkish-advance-1956435883|title=Russia bombs IS-held town in Syria, aids Turkish advance|publisher=Middle East Eye|date=29 December 2016|accessdate=29 December 2016|archive-date=2017-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171113060412/http://www.middleeasteye.net/news/russia-bombs-islamic-state-held-town-syria-aids-turkish-advance-1956435883|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==2017年==
[[File:Albab2.png|thumb]]
2017年1月15日有報道稱土耳其陸軍在巴卜之戰中已損失約10輛[[豹2型坦克|豹2型坦克]]。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://mil.news.sina.com.cn/2017-01-16/doc-ifxzqnip1422150.shtml |title=豹-2坦克不败金身被破 土耳其被IS连干掉10辆 |publisher=新浪網 |date=2017-01-16 |accessdate=2017-01-23 |archive-date=2017-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202022337/http://mil.news.sina.com.cn/2017-01-16/doc-ifxzqnip1422150.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

敘利亞陸軍的[[老虎部隊|老虎部隊]]在2017年1月17日攻佔巴卜以南的一條村。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://southfront.org/syrian-army-makes-first-gains-anti-isis-operation-south-al-bab/ |title=Syrian Army makes first gains in anti-ISIS operation south of al-Bab |work=South Front |date=2017-01-18 |accessdate= |archive-date=2021-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110052956/https://southfront.org/syrian-army-makes-first-gains-anti-isis-operation-south-al-bab/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>美軍宣稱在巴卜附近針對伊斯蘭國進行空襲。<ref name=USstrikes>{{cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSKBN151350 |title=U.S. carries out strikes near Syria's al-Bab after Turkish criticism |work=Reuters |date=2017-01-17 |accessdate=2017-01-17 |archive-date=2021-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210222135244/https://www.reuters.com/article/idUSKBN151350 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在1月22日晚至23日凌晨，土耳其軍在巴卜地區打死65名伊斯蘭國武裝分子。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2017-01/23/c_1120370572.htm |title=土耳其军方称在叙北部打死65名“伊斯兰国”武装分子 |publisher=新華網 |date=2017-01-23 |accessdate=2017-01-23 |archive-date=2017-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171013144910/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2017-01/23/c_1120370572.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>
[[File:Albab3.png|thumb]]

至2月9日上午，土耳其聯軍已攻佔巴卜市的北部，伊斯蘭國在市內的武裝人員仍有約1,000人，在外圍有約800人。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.voanews.com/a/under-seige-al-bab-islamic-state-faces-retreat-to-raqqa/3716714.html |title=Under Siege in al-Bab, IS Faces Retreat to Raqqa |publisher=美國之音 |date=2017-02-09 |accessdate=2017-02-10 |archive-date=2019-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190422054840/https://www.voanews.com/a/under-seige-al-bab-islamic-state-faces-retreat-to-raqqa/3716714.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>同日俄羅斯戰機誤炸在巴卜地區作戰的土耳其軍隊，造成三名土耳其軍人喪生，俄羅斯總統[[弗拉基米尔·弗拉基米罗维奇·普京|普京]]致電土耳其總統[[雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安|埃爾多安]]，對誤炸事件致歉。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2017/02-10/8145837.shtml |title=土耳其3名士兵被俄战机误炸身亡 普京就此致歉 |publisher=中新網 |date=2017-02-10 |accessdate=2017-02-10 |archive-date=2017-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170209215807/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2017/02-10/8145837.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2月10日，敘利亞政府軍收復巴卜市以南的Abou Taltal村，距離巴卜市不到2公里。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/map-syrian-arab-army-approaches-al-bab-within-2-km-latest-advance/ |title=Map: Syrian Arab Army approaches al-Bab to within 2 km after latest advance |date=2017-02-11 |access-date=2017-02-11 |archive-date=2017-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170515064406/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/map-syrian-arab-army-approaches-al-bab-within-2-km-latest-advance/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2月11日，俄羅斯外交部宣稱敘利亞政府軍在俄羅斯空軍支援下收復塔代夫（Tadef）鎮。俄方宣稱敘政府軍在塔代夫的攻勢消滅650名武裝分子及兩輛坦克。敘政府軍在到達預定的分隔政府軍和反對派的接觸線後停止向巴卜推進。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.voanews.com/a/turkey-backed-syrian-rebel-push-into-islamic-state-held-al-bab/3719386.html |title=Syrian Army, Rebel Forces Converge on Northern City of al-Bab |publisher=美國之音 |date=2017-02-11 |accessdate=2017-02-12 |archive-date=2017-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170606163449/https://www.voanews.com/a/turkey-backed-syrian-rebel-push-into-islamic-state-held-al-bab/3719386.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
[[File:Albab4.png|thumb]]
2月23日，土耳其領導的聯軍攻佔巴卜。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2017-02/24/c_129494694.htm |title=叙利亚反政府武装夺取极端组织“伊斯兰国”重要据点 |publisher=新華網 |date=2017-02-24 |accessdate=2017-02-24 |archive-date=2017-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170227092353/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2017-02/24/c_129494694.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>2月24日，敘利亞反政府武裝在[[巴卜|巴卜]]附近的一個指揮中心遭到疑似由[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]發動的自殺式汽車炸彈襲擊，造成至少60人喪生。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2017/02-24/8159102.shtml |title=叙反对派收复巴卜后遭自杀炸弹袭击 已致60人死 |publisher=中新網 |date=2017-02-24 |accessdate=2017-02-26 |archive-date=2017-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170225052650/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2017/02-24/8159102.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2月26日，敘利亞國營電視台報道敘政府軍收復巴卜以南的塔代夫鎮，<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.voanews.com/a/syrian-forces-aleppo/3740444.html |title=Monitor: Syrian Army Advances Against Islamic State Near Aleppo |publisher=美國之音 |date=2017-02-26 |accessdate=2017-02-26 |archive-date=2018-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180807122501/https://www.voanews.com/a/syrian-forces-aleppo/3740444.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>俄羅斯方面曾在2月11日宣稱敘政府已收復塔代夫。
